BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260327T092400
DTEND:20260327T120600
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-2.941ft at 09:24\n-0.028ft at 12:06\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Easing blend of mid-period SW swell and shorter-period\, steep-angled NW s
 well for waves mainly running thigh to stomach high in the morning\, as be
 st combo breaks see better sets. Surf backs off a bit during the afternoon
  along with the fading swell. Dawn patrol is slowed by an early AM high ti
 de. Mid day gets drained by a negative low tide. \n\nLight/variable winds 
 through the morning\, turning light+ SW in the afternoon for some texture.
  
END:VEVENT
